\begin_inset Formula $w_{21}=\$1$
\end_inset

.
 Then, we have the following data:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{10}(0,0,0)=\alpha_{1}+\delta_{0}+u_{10}$
\end_inset

